Simple tcp-socket server, that can broadcast incoming messages to connected sockets.

Start server with:

# Default host is 'localhost'
# Default port is 3001

$ ruby chat_runner <host> <port>

In new console:

$ telnet <host> <port>

----------------------

It was found here: https://www6.software.ibm.com/developerworks/education/l-rubysocks/l-rubysocks-a4.pdf. 